                  </center><font color="#FFFF00">Welcome to the DDL & OTP list!</font> The DDL is actually a pretty complex thing (and the program that now runs it is one of the most challenging that I've ever written). So I recommend that you read the <a href="/ddl/faq.htm">DDL Frequently Asked Questions</a> if you are at all confused about the process, abbreviations, or anything else.
